###### 66. 使用哪个构造函数可以成功继承`Dog`类?

```javascript
class Dog {
  constructor(name) {
    this.name = name;
  }
};

class Labrador extends Dog {
  // 1 
  constructor(name, size) {
    this.size = size;
  }
  // 2
  constructor(name, size) {
    super(name);
    this.size = size;
  }
  // 3
  constructor(size) {
    super(name);
    this.size = size;
  }
  // 4 
  constructor(name, size) {
    this.name = name;
    this.size = size;
  }

};
